$TGCB here is what REALLY makes stocks trade higher over the long term: 
 
1- Management under promises and over delivers. 
2- Revenue and earnings beat estimates every quarter. (You can't miss by even a penny) 
3- Beat and Raise guidance consistently. 
 
Wall St. Analysts do not like surprises unless it is an upside surprise. Management teams that give modest guidance then deliver better than expected results consistently, create tremendous wealth for investors over time.
